description:
One Kings Lane is the leading online destination for the home. Every day, we launch new sales offering exceptional value on top-brand, vintage, and designer items. Shop everything from furniture and lighting to bedding and gifts to decorative accessories and amazing one–of–a–kind finds.
 
SHOP AT HOME OR ON THE GO
- Fast and fluid browsing on your iPad, iPhone, and iPod touch
- Big and beautiful images highlight product details
- Streamlined checkout for faster, easier shopping
- Our search feature makes finding what you’re looking for a breeze 
- Filters help you narrow down the options when you want something specific
- Categories enable you to focus on the products you want  
 
DAILY SALES
Every day of the week, we launch new sales with incredible savings on furniture, rugs, kitchenware, decor, art, bed and bath, gifts, and more from top brands.
 
TASTEMAKER TAG SALES  
Get direct access to unique pieces from the personal collections of today’s leading design visionaries. Also in the mix: sales featuring authentic props straight from the set of new movies and television shows.
 
VINTAGE & MARKET FINDS
A vibrant marketplace of one–of–a–kind finds. We’ve hand-selected designers and antiques dealers from across the country to create a vast and eclectic mix—with hundreds of items added daily!

releaseNotes:
- Start saving the items that you love with our Favorites feature!  Tap the heart icon to save your favorite items so that you can easily find them again in the app as well as on your computer or tablet.
- We’ve added lots of new information to product pages to enhance your shopping experience.  Be sure to scroll down to check out similar items you might like below the product information!  
- We’ve been busy working on lots of things behind the scenes that will pave the way for more new and exciting features. Stay tuned! 
- Bug fixes? Check. We got ‘em. 

Love our app? Please write a review for us in the App Store. 
Want to help us make the app even better?  Email us your feedback at app@onekingslane.com
